{
  "2376450": {
    "name": "Lighthouse Of The Souls (LOTS)",
    "steam_appid": 2376450,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/ee27019dd917841a531da0520aa508e1.avif?t=1771527995\" width=896 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LIGHTHOUSE OF THE SOULS 是一款第三人称动作 Roguelite 游戏，融合了 Hack and Slash 与 RPG 机制，设定在一个黑暗而超自然的幻想世界中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏拥有写实风格的画面、强烈的氛围感，以及鲜明的类魂（Soulslike）体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不断变化的挑战中，独自一人或与最多 4 名玩家进行在线合作，迎接试炼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/5307e2d287c882814a2143a035f07547.avif?t=1771527995\" width=896 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一座黑暗幻想之岛，隐藏着一座连接生者世界与冥界的破败桥梁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里残留着古老文明的遗迹，他们曾崇拜黑暗守护者，并通过仪式引导迷失的灵魂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位被痛苦与执念驱使的堕落红衣主教，再次打开了世界之间的门户，释放出吞噬整座岛屿的腐化之力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六位拥有不同背景与战斗风格的英雄被吸引至此，踏上净化腐化、揭示真相的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >叙事以环境与氛围为核心，通过探索、敌人设计以及散落在世界各处的故事碎片逐步展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在岛屿的道德衰败中求生，并直面反派陨落背后的悲剧，情感共鸣由此诞生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/7ae1e465dca36faf49b63818b58e6868.avif?t=1771527995\" width=896 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从六名可游玩英雄中选择，每位角色都拥有独特的背景、战斗风格与技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的角色鼓励多样化的玩法选择，提升实验性与重复游玩的价值。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 武士 • 瑞士近卫兵 • 驱魔人 • 拉科塔战士 • 高乔人 • 少林武僧 • </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/c6bf62ec207959a4a7e8390c4070249a.poster.avif?t=1771527995\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/c6bf62ec207959a4a7e8390c4070249a.webm?t=1771527995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/c6bf62ec207959a4a7e8390c4070249a.mp4?t=1771527995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/087dceddf91f590bc49af426d7fe7648.avif?t=1771527995\" width=896 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LOTS 提供四种递进式难度，影响敌人的行为、整体氛围以及危险感知：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >休闲：为新玩家设计，压力较低</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >普通：世界开始反击，游荡的灵魂追踪你的进度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >困难：腐化加剧，红衣主教开始主动追猎</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极限：终极试炼，更多敌人、持续负面效果，以及每一步都至关重要的抉择</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/137451aeccd1539cef6a74f412803e19.poster.avif?t=1771527995\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/137451aeccd1539cef6a74f412803e19.webm?t=1771527995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/137451aeccd1539cef6a74f412803e19.mp4?t=1771527995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更高难度将解锁更丰富的敌人种类、更优的奖励与成就。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/9a2b53f394070998c23df36cd4358ff2.avif?t=1771527995\" width=896 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持最多 4 人的在线合作模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序生成地图与动态任务，每次游戏都会重塑世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于剧情的独特任务与迷你 Boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永久死亡机制</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次冒险都截然不同，迫使玩家不断适应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/2035bdc426a40cc9273fee5db2afc384.avif?t=1771527995\" width=896 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每一局游戏中，你将获得灵魂、金币与卡牌，这些卡牌会以增益或惩罚的形式改变角色属性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在局外进程中，可以解锁永久升级、新英雄以及长期成长内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/0132c1a67db1959f0a129794bfcd5624.avif?t=1771527995\" width=896 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗系统快速、直接且富有挑战性：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强调反应速度与站位的实时 Hack and Slash 战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可多阶段升级的武器，解锁更高伤害与特殊效果</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >会随游戏进程进化的技能系统，让每一局玩法都不同</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376450/extras/eff73df9cd21bcb109d7f53f9cf38ebc.avif?t=1771527995\" width=896 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LIGHTHOUSE OF THE SOULS 仍处于持续开发阶段，并会随着每次更新不断进化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家的反馈对平衡调整、内容扩展以及最终体验的打磨至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们，探索这座岛屿，帮助我们共同塑造想要创造的世界 🕯️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 韩语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 日语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 阿拉伯语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
